Package org.metaborg.spoofax.shell.commands

Contains the logic for executing expressions using the core, or executing commands which are common accross frontends.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ICommandInvoker
    An interface for binding and executing IReplCommands.
    IReplCommand
    Interface for REPL commands.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AnalyzeCommand
    Represents an analyze command sent to Spoofax.
    EvaluateCommand
    Represents an evaluate command sent to Spoofax.
    HelpCommand
    Shows descriptions of all commands, or one command if given.
    ParseCommand
    Represents a parse command sent to Spoofax.
    SpoofaxCommand
    Command for processing a String as an expression in some language.
    SpoofaxCommandInvoker
    Default implementation of an ICommandInvoker.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    CommandNotFoundException
    Thrown when a IReplCommand has not been found.
